
Whenever we try to learn to something about a topic their are generally two method one could follow :

1. he/she will memorise everything about topic --Memorizing
2. he/she will try to understand concept behind that topic -- Generalising

Instance Based :
****************

No concept of training and learning  model, whenever new points comes we react accordingly.
Focus on Similarity 
Example :
KNN Algorithm
Kernel Function


Model Based Learning: model is set of parameter :
*********************

try to draw mathemetical function /try to draw curve.
decision function -- classify new point.
you dont require data points as you have learn pattern.

Example:
Linear Regressor
Logistic Regressor
Decision Tree

